  "memoryTenWordVerbalTrial3": "Verbal Trial 3",
  "memoryTenWordDelayedRecall": "Verbal Delayed Recall",
  "memoryTenWordRecognition": "Verbal Recognition",
  "memoryTenWordScrollInstruction": "Scroll down to reveal more instructions",
  "memoryTenWordTrial1PatientInstruction": "\"I am going to read you a list of 10 words. Remember these words, as I will ask you what you can remember afterwards. Please repeat each word after I have said it, so that I can be sure that you have heard it correctly. Do you understand? Are you ready? Let's go!\"",
  "memoryTenWordRepeatWordInstruction": "If the patient does not repeat the word say: \"Please repeat the word.\" Read the words from left to right. Carry on with the rest of the list.",
  "memoryTenWordWhatWereThoseWords": "\"What were those words?\"",
  "memoryTenWordReadWordsInstruction": "Read the words aloud again from left to right, asking for repetition after every word.",
  "memoryTenWordTapRecalledInstruction": "Tap on each word correctly recalled.",
  "memoryTenWordRememberLaterInstruction": "\"Now try to remember the words because I will ask you again later.\"",
  "memoryTenWordIntermissionInstruction": "Allow about 5 minutes to pass by using distraction tasks such as Months Backwards, Design Fluency and/or Luria Alternating Hand Movements.",
  "memoryTenWordDelayedRecallInstruction": "\"Tell me the words you learned during this memory test.\"",
  "memoryTenWordRecognitionPatientInstruction": "\"I am now going to read a list of words. Some of the words are from the list that I asked you to remember and some of the words are new. Say yes if you recognise the word and no if it was not in the list I asked you to memorise. If you don't know the answer just guess.\"",
  "memoryTenWordRecognitionExaminerInstruction": "The instructions may be repeated if forgotten. To select correct responses, tap on Yes or No for each word. (Words from the original memory list are in BOLD.)",
  "memoryTenWordScoreSummary": "Score Summary",
  "memoryTenWordWorkingMemoryLabel": "Working Memory:",
  "memoryTenWordShortTermMemoryLabel": "Short-Term Memory:",

